Mission reports are three different items, all used in the Cold War quest. They are:

  • Mission report (Ardougne), given to the player by a Penguin in Ardougne Zoo after greeting him.
  • Mission report (Lumbridge), given to the player by the penguins dressed as a sheep after giving them the secret phrase.
  • Mission report (Fake), given to the player by Noodle after trading him swamp tar and 5 feathers.
